    "For Personalized Movie Tagging (LaMP 2), we measure Accuracy (Acc.)",
    "and F-1 Score (F-1).",
    "For Personalized Product Rating (LaMP 3), we assess performance using Mean Absolute Error (MAE) and Root Mean Squared Error (RMSE).",
    "For Personalized Tweet Paraphrasing (LaMP 7), we apply the ROUGE-1 (R-1) and ROUGE-L (R-L) metrics.",
